        <mxCell id="p1" parent="personas_container" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=8;spacingRight=8;spacingTop=6;fillColor=#e8eaf6;strokeColor=#3949ab;fontSize=11;" value="&lt;b&gt;Enterprise App Team&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;i&gt;Stateful IaaS consumers&lt;/i&gt;&lt;hr size=&#39;1&#39;&gt;• Lift-and-shift workloads&lt;br&gt;• Traditional DB / middleware&lt;br&gt;• Need patching, backup, DR&lt;br&gt;• Low cloud maturity&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Wants:&lt;/b&gt; Managed VM + storage" vertex="1">
